    • insertCostes

      public void insertCostes(Map<String,Double> costes, String idCurso)
      insertCostes. This method will insert the colectivo/costes according to the View's table.
      If a given colectivo is not featured in the database, it will be added automatically.
      Parameters:
      costes - Map of Colectivo Name, Colectivo cost for the curso.
      idCurso - Id of the curso.
